Google tasks is an extension for the use of Google's service

Functionality:
 - Google apps gesture
 - Easy switch google apps / normal account
 - Open tasks in new window
 - Browser action configuration
 - Open canvas gestion

v1.5.0 changelog
 - Remove popin option (compatibility with xml builded pages broken)
 - Switch to android tasks view (alert crash on new list creation)
 - Tasks coutner
 - Change name for Google guidelines

v1.5.1 changelog
 - Add scroll for long android tasks list
 - Still wishing an answer for standard mode crash

v1.5.2 changelog
 - Add choice android or standard window

v1.5.3 changelog
 - Add choice to show counter or not
